VALUES ('Word embedding', 'Historically, one of the main limitations of static word embeddings or word vector space models is that words with multiple meanings are conflated into a single representation (a single vector in the semantic space). In other words, polysemy and homonymy are not handled properly. For example, in the sentence "The club I tried yesterday was great!", it is not clear if the term club is rel', TO_VECTOR(TO_CLOB('[0.08926889, -0.11889203, 0.01622205, -0.04557029, -0.03654337, 0.05742822, -0.00580372, -0.00335913, 0.03828627, -0.00799154, 0.04121605, 0.00950112, 0.11860395, 0.05656346, 0.03830678, 0.04479673, -0.01394983, 0.04617521, -0.04346068, 0.01821417, 0.03909481, -0.02067433, -0.04407740, -0.07395642, 0.00128996, -0.02222354, -0.06974170, -0.01470297, 0.04106718, 0.04980791, 0.00845326, 0.08736370, -0.02316700, 0.11622986, -0.01416575, 0.01634836, -0.05190035, 0.00081241, 0.00769744, 0.02186419, -0.02441890, -0.00235051, -0.01694991, 0.03246614, 0.04678750, 0.00374432, -0.00404909, 0.00278671, -0.00052939, 0.03115638, -0.03066303, -0.06326917, 0.06846672, 0.00288752, -0.04167994, 0.01325063, -0.03949808, 0.05605659, -0.03311845, -0.05381717, 0.00919199, 0.02023660, -0.00766177, 0.00237345, 0.01280022, -0.06838346, -0.03330981, 0.07634521, -0.02520906, 0.08685704, -0.00996485, 0.07566389, -0.07154253, -0.04069366, -0.07709190, 0.11195274, 0.07011443, -0.00767983, 0.11779957, -0.07501364, -0.02570264, 0.03298117, 0.04115155, -0.06833976, 0.07725871, 0.04053665, 0.00646905, -0.05278790, -0.06234537, -0.00202842, 0.00123046, -0.08431694, 0.11823739, -0.03383413, 0.05014038, -0.06667826, 0.04920361, 0.02624195, 0.01354804, 0.03725836, 0.01289956, 0.09635707, 0.01187900, -0.07274175, -0.03732974, -0.06041571, -0.01911448, 0.02834207, -0.01049248, -0.07745989, -0.09671972, 0.03908246, 0.04521983, 0.00213457, -0.02447484, -0.01032826, -0.00737946, -0.00352166, 0.07290593, -0.02645710, -0.12030492, 0.05873622, 0.04949041, 0.08112736, -0.03592089, 